<p class="p">To characterize the change in moisture stress, we calculated temporal trends in maximum cumulative water deficit (MCWD—Aragão et al., 
 <xref rid="gcb14413-bib-0002" ref-type="ref" class="xref">2007</xref>) for each plot. MCWD represents the most negative value of water deficit (wd), that is, the difference between precipitation (
 <italic class="italic">P</italic>) and evapotranspiration (
 <italic class="italic">E</italic>) within each year, where for each month (
 <italic class="italic">n</italic>) wd is quantified as: 
 <disp-formula id="gcb14413-disp-0001" class="disp-formula">
  <label class="label">(1)</label>
  <math id="nlm-math-1" class="math">
   <mrow class="mrow">
    <mrow class="mrow">
     <mtable class="mtable">
      <mtr class="mtr">
       <mtd class="mtd"/>
       <mtd columnalign="left" class="mtd">
        <mrow class="mrow">
         <mi mathvariant="normal" class="mi">If</mi>
         <mspace width="0.166667em" class="mspace"/>
         <msub class="msub">
          <mi mathvariant="normal" class="mi">wd</mi>
          <mrow class="mrow">
           <mi mathvariant="normal" class="mi">n</mi>
           <mo class="mo">−</mo>
           <mn class="mn">1</mn>
          </mrow>
         </msub>
         <mo class="mo">−</mo>
         <msub class="msub">
          <mi class="mi">E</mi>
          <mi mathvariant="normal" class="mi">n</mi>
         </msub>
         <mo class="mo">+</mo>
         <msub class="msub">
          <mi class="mi">P</mi>
          <mi mathvariant="normal" class="mi">n</mi>
         </msub>
         <mo class="mo">&lt;</mo>
         <mn class="mn">0</mn>
         <mo class="mo">;</mo>
        </mrow>
       </mtd>
      </mtr>
      <mtr class="mtr">
       <mtd class="mtd"/>
       <mtd columnalign="left" class="mtd">
        <mrow class="mrow">
         <mi mathvariant="normal" class="mi">then</mi>
         <mspace width="0.277778em" class="mspace"/>
         <msub class="msub">
          <mi mathvariant="normal" class="mi">wd</mi>
          <mi mathvariant="normal" class="mi">n</mi>
         </msub>
         <mo class="mo">=</mo>
         <msub class="msub">
          <mi mathvariant="normal" class="mi">wd</mi>
          <mrow class="mrow">
           <mi mathvariant="normal" class="mi">n</mi>
           <mo class="mo">−</mo>
           <mn class="mn">1</mn>
          </mrow>
         </msub>
         <mo class="mo">−</mo>
         <msub class="msub">
          <mi class="mi">E</mi>
          <mi mathvariant="normal" class="mi">n</mi>
         </msub>
         <mo class="mo">+</mo>
         <msub class="msub">
          <mi class="mi">P</mi>
          <mi mathvariant="normal" class="mi">n</mi>
         </msub>
        </mrow>
       </mtd>
      </mtr>
      <mtr class="mtr">
       <mtd class="mtd"/>
       <mtd columnalign="left" class="mtd">
        <mrow class="mrow">
         <mi mathvariant="normal" class="mi">else</mi>
         <mspace width="0.166667em" class="mspace"/>
         <msub class="msub">
          <mi mathvariant="normal" class="mi">wd</mi>
          <mi mathvariant="normal" class="mi">n</mi>
         </msub>
         <mo class="mo">=</mo>
         <mn class="mn">0</mn>
        </mrow>
       </mtd>
      </mtr>
     </mtable>
    </mrow>
    <mo class="mo">.</mo>
   </mrow>
  </math>
 </disp-formula>
</p>
